# Codegen workspace

This repo builds a **CLI coding agent** (OpenAI, workspace tools, phased delivery).

## Read first

- **[AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md)** at the repo root — full decisions and conventions.
- **[docs/codegen_requirements.md](docs/codegen_requirements.md)** — FR/NFR, architecture, phases.
- **[docs/codegen_stories.md](docs/codegen_stories.md)** — backlog and story format.

## Non-negotiables for implementation

- **CLI only**; **OpenAI** for the model; **color console** (Claude-style), `NO_COLOR` / non-TTY safe.
- Prefer **OpenAI SDK + explicit tool loop** so the code stays easy to learn and inspect. Do not default to LangGraph/LangChain unless the user or a story explicitly requires it.
- Respect **workspace root** boundaries, **plan vs execute**, and **policy** for shell commands when those stories apply.

## When editing stories or specs

Keep **phase tags**, **acceptance criteria**, and **maps to** requirement IDs consistent with `codegen_requirements.md`.
